'''Zehethbra''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[ZeHethbra]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[ZeHeth/Legends|ZeHeth]]. It included snarls, growls, chitters, and angry shrieks, among other features.

Most ZeHethbra were fluent in both the Zehethbra language and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], although they were only literate in their own language.

